Optional : https://www.lisenet.com/2017/centos-7-server-hardening-guide/

Install necessary packages 

yum install vim bash-completion net-tools wget curl lsof unzip

 Remove unnecessary packages

yum remove postfix chrony alsa-* ivtv-* iwl*firmware aic94xx-firmware*

 Clean your repositories and cache 

yum clean all && rm -rf /var/cache/yum && yum makecache fast
 
 Finally update your OS

yum update
